OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FBrighter spells likely at
OL,6,Ffirst, and soon feeling warm in any
OL,7,Fsunshine. Cloud then thickens during
OL,8,Fthe afternoon, with outbreaks of light
OL,9,Frain possible later.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FCloudy a t first with patchy
OL,12,Flight rain becoming partly cloudy
OL,13,Fovernight and settled with winds
OL,14,Fgradually easing and cooler overnight
OL,15,Ftemperatures, with mist and fog
OL,16,Fpatches possible.
OL,17,
OL,18,CFriday:FChilly start Friday then sunny
OL,19,Fintervals, cloud thickening later with
OL,20,Fthe chance of rain overnight. Winds
OL,21,Fremain blustery along the coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
