OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FRain
OL,6,Fand strong winds Saturday morning,
OL,7,Fisolated showers later. Sunshine and
OL,8,Fshowers Sunday. Monday brings
OL,9,Fwidespread showers. Temperatures near
OL,10,Faverage for April.
